      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "The user was unable or unwilling to provide their mailing address.\n \nPolitely let them know that you may need this information to complete the booking, and offer alternatives:\n- They can call back when they have the information ready\n\nAsk if there's anything else you can help with.\nIf they still decline after being reassured, let them know that's okay and move on.\nDo not ask more than two times total for any piece of information."
      }
